metadata.name: Aggregate Pass Key
metadata.description:
The Aggregate Pass Key is the ultimate ticket into a token gated membership which provides multitudes of industries aggregated in one place. 

The Aggregate Pass Key will be burnable into a specific category pass. 

The pass will give you access to the chosen category's aggregated content.

Once minting of the Aggregate Pass Key finishes, no further keys will be issued.

The first burn event will be for the News Pass, aggregating all the top news networks in one place for an easily digestible content format. 

After the News Pass, is the Adult Pass, access to the top premium adult network content.

Following passes will be community voted.

Remember, 1 Aggregate Pass Key = 1 Content Pass, content passes are not exchangeable so once burned it is permanent.

Open Edition time period decided by AI using factors such as gas, mint frequency and twitter interactions.
